OL,3,CFormer England captain Serena Keren
OL,4,CGuthrie elected as Jersey Senator.
OL,6,FFormer England netball captain Serena
OL,7,FKersten Guthrie has been elected as
OL,8,Fone of Jersey's nine Senators.
OL,10,FDeputy-Elect Guthrie's international
OL,11,Fplaying career spanned almost 15
OL,12,Fyears, and she was voted Jersey
OL,13,FSportsperson of the Year in 2014.
OL,15,FNow, the Commonwealth Games gold
OL,16,Fmedallist is turning her attention to
OL,17,Fa new arena- a political one.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
