FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781118693
OL,3,CFormer England captain Serena Keren
OL,4,CGuthrie elected as Jersey Senator.
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News, Deputy-Elect
OL,7,FGuthrie said she is "massively
OL,8,Fhumbled", and compared her newfound
OL,9,Fpolitical success with her well-
OL,10,Fdocumented sporting accomplishments:
OL,11,F"I probably put this up there with
OL,12,Fplaying for England. It's an
OL,13,Fincredible privilege to lead in this
OL,14,Fway for an island that I absolutely
OL,15,Flove."
OL,17,FDeputy-Elect Guthrie wants to prove to
OL,18,Fyoung people that they should not feel
OL,19,Fboxed in, but should be flexible and
OL,20,Fopen to new avenues.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781118693
OL,3,CFormer England captain Serena Keren
OL,4,CGuthrie elected as Jersey Senator.
OL,6,FShe told ITV News: "You can change
OL,7,Fdirection in your career, you can
OL,8,Fpivot and go and do something else...
OL,9,FI never thought I'd be doing this in
OL,10,Fmy entire life but I also never
OL,11,Fthought I'd be captaining England and
OL,12,Fwinning gold medals, but here I am."
OL,14,FShe celebrated her return to a high-
OL,15,Fpressure environment, expressing
OL,16,Fexcitement for the challenge of being
OL,17,Fback in a role where she will not be
OL,18,Fthe most experienced.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781118693
OL,3,CFormer England captain Serena Keren
OL,4,CGuthrie elected as Jersey Senator.
OL,6,FAsked about the emphasis she has
OL,7,Fplaced upon teamwork in her manifesto,
OL,8,FDeputy-Elect Guthrie said: "I want to
OL,9,Fbe able to work with people to
OL,10,Funderstand the value of how working
OL,11,Fwith others can achieve great things.
OL,13,F"You've got 49 brains in there (the
OL,14,FState Assembly). That is always going
OL,15,Fto be better than one, and one person
OL,16,Ftaking all the weight on their
OL,17,Fshoulders. The complex issues we have
OL,18,Fin Jersey at the moment are really
OL,19,Finterconnected so we're going to need
OL,20,Fto leverage absolutely everything we
OL,21,Fhave."
OL,26,@uD@`pmvD@Opn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781118693
OL,3,CFormer England captain Serena Keren
OL,4,CGuthrie elected as Jersey Senator.
OL,6,FShe continued: "Teamwork can be at the
OL,7,Fforefront of getting the island back
OL,8,Fon track."
OL,10,FThe former England captain also
OL,11,Fclarified that she would love a role
OL,12,Fas Sports Minister, but expressed that
OL,13,Fshe would be interested in expanding
OL,14,Fthis into a position working as
OL,15,FMinister for Sports and Communities.
OL,17,FDeputy-Elect Guthrie told ITV News
OL,18,F"the charitable sector is deep in need
OL,19,Fof more advocacy, and maybe a Minister
OL,20,Fto be that person to represent them."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1781118693
OL,3,CFormer England captain Serena Keren
OL,4,CGuthrie elected as Jersey Senator.
OL,6,FAll four female candidates for Senator
OL,7,Fwere successful in their campaigns-
OL,8,F something Deputy-Elect Guthrie
OL,9,Fcelebrates.
OL,11,F"It's huge... You need balance, it's
OL,12,Fabout representation. I'm a true
OL,13,Fbeliever that if we want to create
OL,14,Frobust policies and legislation that
OL,15,Fis sustainable, you need different
OL,16,Fviews, and people in the room to be
OL,17,Fable to do that."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
